  "detailed_description": "<strong>Somewhere, deep in the American wheat belt, a shadow looms. <br>Are you sure you're alone?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214840/extras/3ebe15ba4dfa99112521a51784e201fc.avif?t=1669210041\" width=800 height=160 /></span><br><br><br>You're working at a petrol station in the middle of nowhere. It's late at night, nobody else around. Something feels off. <br>You ignore that feeling and continue with your tasks.A car pulls up and honks, beckoning you to come over. <br>You can feel the creeping dread surround you, but you try to ignore it...<br><br>A short 10-15 minute horror game with multiple endings.",
